snippet.title: Arcade Game: Highway Chase (1980 Data East)
snippet.description:
A galaxian type shooting game where you are in the highway shooting cars on the screen to clear the level.

Gameplay starts at 3:24

Note: Invincibility cheat was used after down to last life.  Re-uploaded due to improvements in graphic emulation for this game. The game is endless so I quit afterwards.
